text: Hello, how are you?
I am good, how are you?
I'm great, have you heard of Save the Children?
A little bit
They are a children's charity, they do a lot for kids.
I do believe in helping the children
Me too, I've been donating to them regularly over the past few years.
Same, I try to give what I can, but it's hard when you are broke
Agreed, we make extra money here for a reason!
exactly! I feel selfish when I can't donate, but the small stuff adds up
I'm glad you and I think the same. One cent definetely helps them out.
Yeah that is true
Well, I plan on donating one cent today. Are you planning to donate?
I think I could do at least 1 cent
Perfect! We could match each other then.
I'd rather volunteer if I could
I understand that, if we could volunteer through this interface instead I probably would as well.
Same, I also like to donate used good too. OLd clothes and stuff
I try to do that as well, there's a Goodwill near me that I donate to.
Yeah, i definitely want to help the kids
